{"tid":1124400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣酒樓天井發現赤祼女屍 警封鎖現場調查","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T10:11:29.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"448dcabd0711302d3b8fe05d1c3cde1d119efe5a","tid":1124400,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣道78號一間酒樓的天井位置發現赤裸女屍，警方封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今早10時許，警方接報指上址有人昏迷，警員趕至時發現一具赤裸女屍，隨即封鎖現場，正循刑事方向調查。據悉，涉事的酒樓正進行裝修，工人早上開工時發現女屍，揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986773-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E8%B5%A4%E7%A5%BC%E5%A5%B3%E5%B1%8D+%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986773-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2593%259C%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BA%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E7%25A5%25BC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B1%258D%2B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=ce10450d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986773-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2593%259C%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BA%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E7%25A5%25BC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B1%258D%2B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=b6b2ff9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986773-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E8%B5%A4%E7%A5%BC%E5%A5%B3%E5%B1%8D+%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%81%E9%